Integrate rest_log with shopfloor_base.

As of today simply provide a shortcut to rest.log records from the
Shopfloor app and allows Shopfloor managers to see logs.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Usage
=====

Go to "Shopfloor / Logs".

